  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a lawless future Europe, you’re the last hope for high-risk deliveries through hostile territory. Climb into your combat car and race across a procedurally generated continent, dodging bullets, crashing through convoys, and outmaneuvering mechanized death. Every run is different.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every route is dangerous, but the pay is good.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DRIVE and DESTROY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Employ precision control and expert driving skills to race rings around foes, dodge incoming projectiles, and unleash intense attacks. High-octane action at every turn, slide and spin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ed3bcf04e04a4ff9737b887e734132a2.poster.avif?t=1761612741\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ed3bcf04e04a4ff9737b887e734132a2.webm?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ed3bcf04e04a4ff9737b887e734132a2.mp4?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MEGA-VEHICLE BOSS BATTLES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat the lawless factions that dominate dystopian future Europe, and take down their insane, heavily-armed boss machines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/2f293637526e8b29c1c029c82950a9b4.poster.avif?t=1761612741\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/2f293637526e8b29c1c029c82950a9b4.webm?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/2f293637526e8b29c1c029c82950a9b4.mp4?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GET PAID and UPGRADE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tackle dangerous delivery missions to ensure the safe arrival of precious cargo. Get paid, and modify your car with offensive, defensive, cosmetic and performance-based customisations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/37ae177939eecc7d2f0353ed5a7cee8e.poster.avif?t=1761612741\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/37ae177939eecc7d2f0353ed5a7cee8e.webm?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLOSIVE DELIVERY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your territory across the post-apocalyptic continent. Only the most skilled Gearshifter can take on the most perilous routes and reach the mysterious Citadel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ce4d2ab83ff3062a3ae8764398f38401.poster.avif?t=1761612741\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ce4d2ab83ff3062a3ae8764398f38401.webm?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ce4d2ab83ff3062a3ae8764398f38401.mp4?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced top-down vehicle combat with tight, responsive controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue-lite progression with random routes, enemies, and gear unlocks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11 deadly factions and mega-boss battles across 9 zones</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ upgradeable parts to customize your combat car</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple difficulty modes, including permadeath for the fearless</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a lawless future Europe, you’re the last hope for high-risk deliveries through hostile territory. Climb into your combat car and race across a procedurally generated continent, dodging bullets, crashing through convoys, and outmaneuvering mechanized death. Every run is different.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every route is dangerous, but the pay is good.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DRIVE and DESTROY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Employ precision control and expert driving skills to race rings around foes, dodge incoming projectiles, and unleash intense attacks. High-octane action at every turn, slide and spin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ed3bcf04e04a4ff9737b887e734132a2.poster.avif?t=1761612741\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ed3bcf04e04a4ff9737b887e734132a2.webm?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ed3bcf04e04a4ff9737b887e734132a2.mp4?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MEGA-VEHICLE BOSS BATTLES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat the lawless factions that dominate dystopian future Europe, and take down their insane, heavily-armed boss machines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/2f293637526e8b29c1c029c82950a9b4.poster.avif?t=1761612741\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/2f293637526e8b29c1c029c82950a9b4.webm?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/2f293637526e8b29c1c029c82950a9b4.mp4?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GET PAID and UPGRADE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tackle dangerous delivery missions to ensure the safe arrival of precious cargo. Get paid, and modify your car with offensive, defensive, cosmetic and performance-based customisations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/37ae177939eecc7d2f0353ed5a7cee8e.poster.avif?t=1761612741\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/37ae177939eecc7d2f0353ed5a7cee8e.webm?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLOSIVE DELIVERY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your territory across the post-apocalyptic continent. Only the most skilled Gearshifter can take on the most perilous routes and reach the mysterious Citadel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ce4d2ab83ff3062a3ae8764398f38401.poster.avif?t=1761612741\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ce4d2ab83ff3062a3ae8764398f38401.webm?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1017160/extras/ce4d2ab83ff3062a3ae8764398f38401.mp4?t=1761612741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced top-down vehicle combat with tight, responsive controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rogue-lite progression with random routes, enemies, and gear unlocks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11 deadly factions and mega-boss battles across 9 zones</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ upgradeable parts to customize your combat car</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple difficulty modes, including permadeath for the fearless</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
